library(shiny); library(shinyMobile); library(shinymanager);library(googledrive); library(googlesheets4); library(shinyjs); library(shinythemes); library(shiny.pwa)
credenciales <- data.frame(user = c("Eva"), # mandatory
                           password = c("MsHSM2024."))

# Opciones de registro ####
set_labels(
  language = "en",
  "Please authenticate" = "Por favor, inicie sesión",
  "Username:" = "Usuario:",
  "Password:" = "Contraseña:",
  "Login" = "Entrar"
)
# Arranque en google drive ####
# Autorización de drive y google
gs4_auth(cache = ".secrets2", email = "enfermeriasantamarina@gmail.com")
drive_auth(cache = ".secrets1", email = "enfermeriasantamarina@gmail.com")

# App ####
ui <- f7Page(
  pwa(
  "https://emekgd-ikerapraiz.shinyapps.io/musica_prueba/",
  title = "MsHSM",
  icon = "assets/icon.png",
  output = "WWW",
  color = "#654321"
),
  useShinyjs(),
  options = list(dark = F, filled = F, theme = "md"),
  useShinyjs(),
  title = div(
    img(src="logo.png", height = "50px"),("Visualización de habitaciones")),
  f7TabLayout(
    navbar = f7Navbar(
      title = div(
        img(src="logo.png", height = "50px"),("Visualización de habitaciones")),
      hairline = T,
      shadow = T,
      leftPanel = F,
      rightPanel = F
    ),
    f7Tabs(
      animated = TRUE,
      f7Tab(
        title = "Visualizar camas",
        tabName = "camas",
        icon = f7Icon("table"),
        active = FALSE,
        f7Shadow(
          intensity = 10,
          hover = T,
          f7Card(
            title = h3("Pulse Ver"),
            f7Button(inputId = "ver", label = "VER", color = "blue")
          )),
        f7Shadow(
          intensity = 10,
          hover = T,
        f7Card(
          title = h3("Habitaciones"),
          uiOutput("tabla")

))))))

ui <- secure_app(ui, theme = shinytheme("simplex"),background  = "linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 255, 0.5),
                       rgba(255, 255, 0, 0.5));")
# Programación ####
server <- function(input, output, session) {
  res_auth <- secure_server(
    check_credentials = check_credentials(credenciales)
  )

observeEvent(input$ver,{
  id_musica <- googledrive::drive_get("intervencion_musical")
  datos <- range_read(id_musica, sheet = "habitaciones")
  output$tabla <- renderUI({
    f7Table(datos)})
})
}

shinyApp(ui, server)
